timelineItems.name: Fire Conf Live
timelineItems.text: 90+'- Qunicy gets sandwiched. Ensuing FK rolls across the six, and Cociș fails to capitalize. #cf97

timelineItems.comment: Attempt missed. Aaron Schoenfeld (Columbus Crew) header from the centre of the box is close, but misses to the right. Assisted by Federico Higuaín with a cross.
Attempt blocked. Mike Magee (Chicago Fire) right footed shot from outside the box is blocked. Assisted by Quincy Amarikwa.
Second Half ends, Chicago Fire 1, Columbus Crew 1.
